條好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前做過part-time<br />\n舖頭好乾淨 啲煲/工具洗唔乾淨會比人屌<br />\n所有嘢食唔會隔夜<br />\n只要發現一舊飯團/一煲湯嘅品質有問題<br />\n全線分店都會dum晒批貨<br />\n所以可以好放心咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本公司係呢方面真係做得幾好<br />\n<br />\n但人工低到得$40一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  九龍區仲要得$38<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜都要做不突止 仲要派傳單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（辭左職成年 前幾日經過見到人工$1蚊都冇加過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\nfull time 仲慘 一星期返六日 每日十個鐘<br />\n都好似得 10k 鬆啲 仲要幾乎零福利咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8b09d12a7c43f3cad1940ee21e32ed2fcfff7c","tid":333051,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好鍾意 明太子沙律 三文魚沙律 北海道秋鮭<br />\n三文魚手卷同加州手卷都好好食 不過成$26條好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前做過part-time<br />\n舖頭好乾淨 啲煲/工具洗唔乾淨會比人屌<br />\n所有嘢食唔會隔夜<br />\n只要發現一舊飯團/一煲湯嘅品質有問題<br />\n全線分店都會dum晒批貨<br />\n所以可以好放心咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本公司係呢方面真係做得幾好<br />\n<br />\n但人工低到得$40一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  九龍區仲要得$38<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜都要做不突止 仲要派傳單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（辭左職成年 前幾日經過見到人工$1蚊都冇加過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\nfull time 仲慘 一星期返六日 每日十個鐘<br />\n都好似得 10k 鬆啲 仲要幾乎零福利咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n奴性重   出最低工資都有人爭住做"},{"pid":"432f27502a7e0aff30694bd5bdc30d107a6e1513","tid":333051,"uid":61910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"稅務大樓個間朝早日日有條龍<br />\n係得個邊返工嘅好多都唔介意貴個十蚊八蚊<br />\n<br />\n不過我都係食燒賣多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼食落唔會一舊粉咁"},{"pid":"811a419da84116af0a52673980897f24c2d7d147","tid":333051,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:02:55.000Z","msg":"屌711都13定14蚊一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢家啲飯係唔錯 但上次果個舊得勁少料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6537086959294af05c2c6fe8fbdd122de983f8","tid":333051,"uid":21234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:05:59.000Z","msg":"好正 每日番工都食佢既早餐"},{"pid":"054b27cd1eb933b2af64acc35e2a1a9778478c1c","tid":333051,"uid":27302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:25:54.000Z","msg":"好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想佢瘋狂開分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645416d4335a8716d9cfbe171ba7a65dfb1ffe41","tid":333051,"uid":42411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:27:44.000Z","msg":"全港最高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個雞湯最正<br />\n飯團就鍾意流心蛋同芥辣八爪魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dc882f0516ef62d91b1bc84c41dacbcb33fd8a","tid":333051,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">明太子淨雞雞換咗差啲嘅料, 新嗰隻腥咗魚子又少咗</span><br />\n酸梅由一pat梅醬變成一粒梅乾, 飯糰中間勁鹹但角落頭完全冇味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然細餸選擇多咗, 但係由$16加到$20個分量就唔值<br />\n個湯就好少少, 叫多渣都可以當半個餸嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲以為得我發覺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前好食好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab085e0abe66c08c990fe80839d6c295821d3af8","tid":333051,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:58:19.000Z","msg":"貴"},{"pid":"8ad03c4b5a9dc3fefcac1feca4c9c0fbadd94211","tid":333051,"uid":14046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:34:54.000Z","msg":"好過7-11好撚多<br />\n想佢係旺角開分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf1ed5be769143986f86cd04d8551b330db8152","tid":333051,"uid":55410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T20:44:38.000Z","msg":"唔就腳 下下都開係商業大廈入面<br />\n不如開多d係地鐵站附近啦"},{"pid":"79bbc1121db35b16ddbc0096de7f89ee597229ca","tid":333051,"uid":4278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T21:18:14.000Z","msg":"個口爆流心蛋爆到我成口都係好撚好食啊屌"},{"pid":"e9856b1351d558a8f28f68a9485a2f29a9061e4b","tid":333051,"uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T21:55:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個口爆流心蛋爆到我成口都係好撚好食啊屌</blockquote><br />\n流心蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9265776e6e50122e6c74860fbf0bbcac93df2310","tid":333051,"uid":49032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T22:34:08.000Z","msg":"幾喜 價錢係香港唔算貴 <br />\n唔明d連登仔點解話貴 十幾蚊當正餐咩on9"},{"pid":"81352fdc2fae350eff851b54b1a1cdea70cc7af7","tid":333051,"uid":49032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T22:34:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾好 價錢係香港唔算貴 <br />\n唔明d連登仔點解話貴 十幾蚊當正餐咩on9</blockquote>"},{"pid":"84491d4a4059ff8a724e54a568710321904760ae","tid":333051,"uid":31713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T22:36:28.000Z","msg":"蒲燒鮭魚好好食"},{"pid":"5c207cf524e2418acc57a594e8537d1a757cee63","tid":333051,"uid":3647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T22:42:15.000Z","msg":"牛肉正囉"},{"pid":"bedaa40bddee997d687520846c8ab14b534149dc","tid":333051,"uid":49976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T22:46:49.000Z","msg":"好鐘意食個便當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80bf6c65f2964609b6fd054208cbd7ca5084fbb6","tid":333051,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T23:50:57.000Z","msg":"d湯好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01808b0a8d6898ba1264bdad8965bcb0c71cc9f6","tid":333051,"uid":5846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T00:06:55.000Z","msg":"一直都好中意食<br />\n<br />\n對比7-11好十萬倍<br />\n<br />\n啲飯唔似7-11咁係雪左幾天仲有陣雪味<br />\n<br />\n啲米咸度啱啱好又多款<br />\n<br />\n唯一問題分店太少，呢間野用日本米根本無得輸，就算日本好多都唔係用日本米！<br />\n<br />\n仲有個豆乳湯都好正<br />\n<br />\n成日講得出唔夠飽唔抵食嘅人一定食開垃圾，佢個質素值呢個價，起碼呢種包裝飯團我夠膽講華御結係香港第一。"},{"pid":"43f255ca9c150eab6a8d4008612e534629746aea","tid":333051,"uid":22833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T00:33:55.000Z","msg":"見到啲係咁話同日本啲便利店差幾皮真心笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己以前係日本讀書 其實華御結除左貴啲啲 同口味真係差唔得幾遠<br />\n我啲㗎佬老細每次翻嚟呢邊做野都會買華御結 都話好食同日本便利店無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a946e59406a202da67dd91d8e9b0dbbb150bf31","tid":333051,"uid":45983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T00:35:50.000Z","msg":"食過一次 認真講 合格<br />\n<br />\n但太貴食唔起"},{"pid":"dcc82b1f68e23ccd0bd9d186c170b2f4ee21de9e","tid":333051,"uid":42152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T00:45:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到啲係咁話同日本啲便利店差幾皮真心笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己以前係日本讀書 其實華御結除左貴啲啲 同口味真係差唔得幾遠<br />\n我啲㗎佬老細每次翻嚟呢邊做野都會買華御結 都話好食同日本便利店無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前都係日本讀書<br />\n但我覺得日本真係好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n華御結中間啲料太少，食到三份一仲係白飯，同埋好多時會斷開兩邊<br />\n不過就好過其他香港嘢囉"},{"pid":"80905ac11190925161b4589b497dd246f9df3742","tid":333051,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T00:49:58.000Z","msg":"每朝會食a餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d49ccedc203222a9b31ba42beb4df4d802f048","tid":333051,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:00:59.000Z","msg":"日本便利店質素，但價錢係2-3倍"},{"pid":"ad11795cbb99c965d6842231cd7aa715271c24af","tid":333051,"uid":84381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:08:02.000Z","msg":"係咪唔係間間都有早餐？<br />\n樓下個到無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8c6f21d69c1d30baed718ac7c568f09e0cc389","tid":333051,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:10:40.000Z","msg":"D野唔差, 飯團之外, 午餐既咖哩飯及湯都OK,就係偏貴<br />\nBTW, 佢都好識招人, 專招妹妹仔, 好好J <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17674e676a756d9660633ac43f60d78c2c088b8","tid":333051,"uid":83215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:10:58.000Z","msg":"平靚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日經過太古地鐵站都會買返公司食"},{"pid":"187630e373cc33a0fc603871e69116e3ba53b4cd","tid":333051,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:11:16.000Z","msg":"肉鬆"},{"pid":"2cb3cdde9341f6403e37c68f9d91bfa49d561904","tid":333051,"uid":60047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:12:43.000Z","msg":"白御結世界第一"},{"pid":"21c32ec6d88efa0193464772cd67406fb06a3fa2","tid":333051,"uid":38711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貴711同ok少少，好食好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地有隻韓式手卷我之前成日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd飯好撚硬但我鐘意食飯團所以都照殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰隻叮咗會好食啲㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898ef5c18a5b15742dec8e2d9c74399809677a24","tid":333051,"uid":95069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:36:58.000Z","msg":"幾年前喺嗰到返過part time <br />\n啲飯團日日新鮮喺火炭工場運過黎 買唔曬都唔會留過夜 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916c6a964123d035e8d0954d1b2005a6423fc65b","tid":333051,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:38:09.000Z","msg":"堅貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2158bb8a8347cd6c8fc80db5a8edefb4c30e81","tid":333051,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:40:12.000Z","msg":"7仔講緊賣13.9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3802cafa2d2a0ded0780c97ecd7f737616ec34","tid":333051,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"返工樓下有間<br />\n<br />\n朝朝都好多人買黎當早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98d65cad5890e5cc9071ad3785fbf42c6de5e5f","tid":333051,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有一排返工日日食<br />\n精選: 明太子沙律 溫泉蛋 鮭<br />\n個白湯好飲</blockquote><br />\nlawson"},{"pid":"9688ef26362cf6471966d74f6ad36d04d18531aa","tid":333051,"uid":24,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:51:59.000Z","msg":"以前係灣仔返工，覺得好貴<br />\n但轉左科學園工後，對比起入面又貴又差既餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就覺得呢個價都唔算離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4628b9441d1d218b2786b14e559f4a69c858a679","tid":333051,"uid":73004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>貴711同ok少少，好食好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地有隻韓式手卷我之前成日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd飯好撚硬但我鐘意食飯團所以都照殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰隻叮咗會好食啲㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中過伏，真係好難食，隔夜冷飯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d85e431cc74ef997022c5549f7d38bf4082197","tid":333051,"uid":4095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>價錢其實ok, 開得都商業區<br />\n附近都係用開四五十蚊食個lunch架啦<br />\n以前返金鐘日日食咁滯<br />\n而家返灣仔冇得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  開多幾間分店就好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n灣仔有三間wor</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三間都唔近我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n稅務大樓叫最近但係行得去再行返公司都唔使食<br />\n開d喺地鐵站會好d"},{"pid":"53bec9f7a51d7cdf0ffdb5bc4dfd236dd4bb9299","tid":333051,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有一排返工日日食<br />\n精選: 明太子沙律 溫泉蛋 鮭<br />\n個白湯好飲</blockquote><br />\nlawson</blockquote><br />\n佢明太子d料愈黎愈少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5690cc1537334b101d68026de66b316f3bc0e4","tid":333051,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>貴711同ok少少，好食好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地有隻韓式手卷我之前成日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd飯好撚硬但我鐘意食飯團所以都照殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰隻叮咗會好食啲㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中過伏，真係好難食，隔夜冷飯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所有7-11同ok嘅都一樣急凍隔夜，唔叮就好撚難食有雪味。啲飯硬好好似冰咁，貼錢都唔食。<br />\n<br />\n叮完都係差華幾條街，啲飯完全唔好食！<br />\n<br />\n華御啲飯係好到淨食飯都得！"},{"pid":"3106a69763bb15ff0368201e5465c1bf4e009dc8","tid":333051,"uid":105766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:32:42.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得佢啲分店都好隔涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 覺得好食 但唔會突登搭車去嗰啲地方買"},{"pid":"ed7a0b7059bb0639489f6c79c072ddb4e8faffd1","tid":333051,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:36:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人覺得佢啲分店都好隔涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 覺得好食 但唔會突登搭車去嗰啲地方買</blockquote><br />\n唔隔涉，金鐘灣仔太古城都算中產旺地段，應該target中產，住九龍就慘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60988b7b8e0c95b71d9c98a7331020d25a47e8e2","tid":333051,"uid":72749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好鍾意 明太子沙律 三文魚沙律 北海道秋鮭<br />\n三文魚手卷同加州手卷都好好食 不過成$26條好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前做過part-time<br />\n舖頭好乾淨 啲煲/工具洗唔乾淨會比人屌<br />\n所有嘢食唔會隔夜<br />\n只要發現一舊飯團/一煲湯嘅品質有問題<br />\n全線分店都會dum晒批貨<br />\n所以可以好放心咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本公司係呢方面真係做得幾好<br />\n<br />\n但人工低到得$40一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  九龍區仲要得$38<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜都要做不突止 仲要派傳單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（辭左職成年 前幾日經過見到人工$1蚊都冇加過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\nfull time 仲慘 一星期返六日 每日十個鐘<br />\n都好似得 10k 鬆啲 仲要幾乎零福利咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n六日人工高少少<br />\n老細仲叫我返多幾日平日熟習吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗咁少人工你返埋我個分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6507307e75d2cac0ba08dd53104f5fd6729c5916","tid":333051,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人覺得佢啲分店都好隔涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 覺得好食 但唔會突登搭車去嗰啲地方買</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔覺 佢係target返office啲人<br />\n我公司5分鐘距離就有"},{"pid":"3ed58f53bc0e44ceec252a9c6b48b0efd6b4f126","tid":333051,"uid":105766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人覺得佢啲分店都好隔涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 覺得好食 但唔會突登搭車去嗰啲地方買</blockquote><br />\n唔隔涉，金鐘灣仔太古城都算中產旺地段，應該target中產，住九龍就慘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我住九龍又唔係過海返office 就算尖沙咀有我都無理由地鐵搭幾個站去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d590b1561ad5b6f15b57e8eaea35ebb273cc27b7","tid":333051,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:25:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人覺得佢啲分店都好隔涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 覺得好食 但唔會突登搭車去嗰啲地方買</blockquote><br />\n唔隔涉，金鐘灣仔太古城都算中產旺地段，應該target中產，住九龍就慘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我住九龍又唔係過海返office 就算尖沙咀有我都無理由地鐵搭幾個站去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets